    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Develop Your Product\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat as a collaborator to help you refine your final presentation.\r\n\r\nYou can share examples, add images or PDFs, and give feedback on AI’s responses to improve its output.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to:\r\n    - Generate ideas, supporting text, dialogue, or other elements for your chosen format\r\n    - Improve the content, structure, or tone of your final product\r\n    - Make your presentation clearer and more engaging\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Tips for Better Results**\r\n- Be specific about your format and audience (e.g., “Write this for a 6th grade audience in the style of a speech”)\r\n- Ask AI to revise for clarity, tone, or voice\r\n- Don’t just accept AI’s first draft—revise and guide it to reflect your ideas\r\n\r\n",
